data.description:
Welcome to this beautiful 4-bedroom, 3-bath home plus a dedicated office/den nestled on a corner lot in Sleepy Hollow! With two nice sized backyards and patios, you'll enjoy outdoor relaxation and entertaining. Inside, the expansive living space provides ample room for gatherings, while the well-appointed bedrooms offer comfort and privacy. 
New roof November 2023!
Priced at $121 sq ft, buyers have room to make this house their home! Seller is also willing to consider a flooring allowance
